thread.title: Emmerdale

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Emmerdale
text: Andy is desperate to vent his anger somewhere tonight so decides to head off on a motorbike scramble with Pete and Finn. However, when they get there, Andy decides he's not arsed with instructions and belts on ahead with Pete tearing after him to try and catch up. It all has pretty dire consequences for Pete though when Andy stops abruptly at a steep drop but Pete doesn't see it coming... oh dear. Meanwhile, Adam tells Victoria that he is going to ask Rakesh what rights he has concerning Johnny's custody. Eh, NONE, he should tell him, because he's not the real father. Dammit Rakesh. Elsewhere, Chas fears what Robert will say when he wakes up, that's IF he wakes up however.
